txt.en: 'I am betting the Enemy have a stockpile of weapons in the city. If we are to recapture Cair Andros for Gondor, we must deplete their weapon caches. This will help us take them by surprise.'
Leading a band of Gondorians, Duinhir, lord of Blackroot Vale, has been tasked with the retaking of Cair Andros.
Weapon-racks can be found around Cair Andros.\n\nYou should destroy weapon-racks.
You have destroyed many weapon-racks in Cair Andros, and have weakened the Enemy foothold on the island fortress.
